    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "76-23-3 \u0026 4\nverior of the dayplane version of the new Douglas D0-6 airliner\n1s shown in this photograph. View 1s looking aft, and cabin entrance\nis adjacent to the curtained cloak room at right.\nLuggage rack over the reclining passenger seats is covered in\nnatural tan leather. At the extreme rear may be seen the club lounge\nhotograp\nwhich seats six persons around a folding-lear table.\nBranitt\nnot to be\nreprodeced\nwith special writ\n- 30- AIRWAYS\nATIO\nTexas",
